'''''Roma wa la n'toura''''' (Icyongereza: '''''Rome Rather Than You'''''; Igifaransa: '''''Rome plutôt que vous''''' ) ni filime y’ikinamico yo muri 2006 yakorewe muri [[Alijeriya]]-[[Igifaransa|abafaransa]] [[Ubudage|n’Ubudage]] iyobowe na Tariq Teguia  ikinwamo na Samira Kaddour na Rachid Amrani nk’urubyiruko babiri bashaka kuva muri Alijeriya n'intambara y'abenegihugu ya Alijeriya kugira ngo bagire ejo hazaza heza<ref>https://www.visionsdureel.ch/en/film/2019/rome-rather-than-you/</ref><ref>https://www.visionsdureel.ch/film/2019/rome-rather-than-you/</ref>.  Nibikorwa bya Teguia byerekanwe bwa mbere.<ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/film/66294/</ref>  (Yabanje gukora filime ngufi na documentaire ya 2002.  ) Filime yatsindiye igihembo cyihariye cyabacamanza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Friborg 2007.<ref>https://www.dohafilminstitute.com/filmfestival/films/rome-rather-than-you</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Kamel w'imyaka 20 n'inshuti ye, Zina w'imyaka makumyabiri n'itatu, bashakisha muri [[Alijeriya]] Bosco ucuruza abantu  kugira ngo babone pasiporo mpimbano kugira ngo bashobore kuva mu gihugu berekeza i Roma<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/28304/rome-rather-than-you</ref>.

== Kwakira ==
''Abanenga ibinyamakuru bitandukanye,'' Robert Koehler yashimye "Umukinnyi wa mbere wa Tariq Teguia.<ref>https://harvardfilmarchive.org/calendar/rome-rather-than-you-2012-10</ref> . . Nubwo ibihe bya nyuma biteganijwe, kugerayo ndetse na nyuma yacyo byerekana Teguia kuba umuyobozi w’amasezerano akomeye "<ref>https://mubi.com/films/rome-rather-than-you</ref>.  Koehler yemeje kandi "ibihangano bisanzwe, byoroshye imikorere" ya Kaddoui na Amrani. <ref>https://www.allmovie.com/movie/rome-rather-than-you-v392802</ref> Mu ''kinyamakuru Slant'', ariko, Eric Henderson yabonaga ko iyi filime "yatekerejwe mu bwirasi, yiyitirira ko yakozwe, kandi ikaba ndende<ref>https://filmstudycenter.fas.harvard.edu/fellows-works/tariq-teguia/</ref>". 

